        "logic": "var calc_output = [];\n\nvar age = parseFloat(age)\nvar smoking = parseFloat(smoking)\nvar dm = parseFloat(dm)\nvar mi = parseFloat(mi)\nvar priorpci = parseFloat(priorpci)\nvar stent = parseFloat(stent)\nvar chf = parseFloat(chf)\nvar veinstent = parseFloat(veinstent)\nvar stentdiameter = parseFloat(stentdiameter)\n\nvar score = age + smoking + dm + mi + priorpci + stent + chf + veinstent + stentdiameter\n\nvar risk, rec\n\nif (score >= 2) {\n\trisk = 'High'\n\trec = 'Prolonged DAPT recommended'\n}\nelse {\n\trisk = 'Low'\n\trec = 'Prolonged DAPT not recommended'\n}\n\n//results\ncalc_output.push({\n    name: 'mini',\n    value: score,\n    value_text: 'points',\n    message: rec\n});\ncalc_output.push({\n    name: 'Score',\n    value: score,\n    value_text: 'points',\n    message: 'DAPT Score'\n});\ncalc_output.push({\n    name: 'risk',\n    value: risk,\n    value_text: 'risk',\n    message: rec\n});",
